 be\ndiscussed, as will the major technical challenges to be overcome to make full\nuse of this powerful instrument. Finally, we show how phase 2 of the SKA could\nprovide a vast increase in the number of detected cosmic rays at the highest\nenergies, and thus to provide new insight into their spectrum and origin.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Aug 2016 12:26:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-09"}
