he accelerator could interrupt operation for years. This\nlecture will provide an overview of the requirements for protection of\naccelerator equipment and introduces various protection systems. Examples are\nmainly from LHC and ESS.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 8 Aug 2016 13:49:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-09"}
